      "briefTitle": "A Study of TX000045 in Patients With Pulmonary Hypertension Secondary to Heart Failure With Preserved Ejection Fraction (the APEX Study)",
      "officialTitle": "A Phase 2, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of TX000045 After 24 Weeks of Treatment in Patients With Pulmonary Hypertension Secondary to Heart Failure With Preserved Ejection Fraction (PH-HFpEF)"
